l Writing textbook in Latvian,Â <em>Juridiska Analize Un Tekstu Rakstisana,</em>Â now in its third edition. Steve was one of the creative forces shaping a new international series of conferences in Applied Legal Storytelling, the first conference being held in London, England, in July 2007, and the second in Portland, Oregon, in July 2009.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"../blackwell-2010-speech\">Read Steve\'s acceptance speechÂ here</a>.", "The 2010 Thomas F. Blackwell Memorial Award Recipient", "", "inherit", "open", "open", "", "422-revision-6", "", "", "2013-02-21 20:04:04", "2013-02-21 20:04:04", "", "422", "http://localhost/alwd.org/422-revision-6/", "0", "revision", "", "0");
