urs of Skills courses (with a grade of at least \"C\" or \"CR\")</li>\n</ul>", "Washburn University School of Law", "", "inherit", "open", "open", "", "969-autosave", "", "", "2013-03-06 18:44:13", "2013-03-06 18:44:13", "", "969", "http://localhost/alwd.org/969-autosave/", "0", "revision", "", "0");
